If in absolute, the positions be changed according to the ancestors? 
Which means, for example, there is a div and the div is in a section div,
then the div will be adjusted according to the section. If the section does not have any position,
then the div inside the section will be positioned according to the body. 

<body>

    <section>
        <h2>Static Demo</h2>
        <div></div>
        <div id="static"></div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Relative Demo</h2>
        <div></div>
        <div id="relative"></div>
        <div></div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Absolute Demo</h2>
        <div></div>
        <div id="absolute"></div>
        <div></div>
    </section>

</body>
